    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 at MRL 2. The simulation package is accepted as providing adequate credibility evidence for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
